room_title: Escape room "We Are Anonymous" by Panic Escape Room in Chicago
review: Great starter escape room.  Exciting and just enough to make it difficult, but not impossible!  I also like how all the stories tie in.

room_title: Escape room "We Are Anonymous" by Panic Escape Room in Chicago
review: I host a once a month escape room meetup!  We enjoyed this game very much! If you guys have any more recommendations, let me know!

room_title: Escape room "We Are Anonymous" by Panic Escape Room in Chicago
